Definition
------------
#variable - kind of brief case 

#function - set of code , we can call whenever needed (DR team , Police)

#data type - different forms , will be store in variables , when create data values , type will be set automatically.

#operator - operate between variables and values

#data structure - keeping data in someorder , in order to retreive as needed basis 

#inbuilt function - some of the functions are readily available in python interpreter

#oops - object = variables+functions

